column12: Details of the murder of the 20 yr old African American transgender woman are still unknown.
Rosa was found dead in her apartment. She had been stabbed in the throat.
Juan was severely beaten causing fractures to the head and face before being run over by a car.

Angie was an 18 year old Latina transgender woman found murdered by Alan Ray Andrade, 31, in her home.

She suffered two severe fractures in her skull. Her family believes that she was murdered because of her gender identity.
